      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW NATULLO (7) is in hot form after clocking a fast 22.17 victory two back then followed up with a 22.87 win at Warragul over 400m last time. Expected to push the clock again here. MINER MICK (4) failed to feature last start at Geelong, but prior to that won by a neck at The Meadows (30.87) beating Swift Gift in a Grade 5 FIN on February 28. Has a solid record from this box including three wins and a minor placing. Likely to play a prominent role. HYLAND AZULA (3) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish 0.8 lengths away in third (22.40) at this track in a Grade 5 over 390m. Will give a great sight again. ISHIKAWA LASS (2) is a last start winner and can go on with it.",
